<span id="freeTextContainer7296110538156640472">i wanted to love this book.<br/>i like it, but i also have <i>issues</i>.<br/><br/>there&apos;s a lot of good things with this book, but it&apos;s equally balanced with things that i didn&apos;t like or just made me question this book. <br/><br/>join us for the liveshow tomorrow!<br/>for now,<br/><b>no thoughts, head empty.</b></span>
